Post.title: Hello World
Post._content:
Welcome to [Hexo](https://hexo.io/)! This is your very first post. Check [documentation](https://hexo.io/docs/) for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in [troubleshooting](https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html) or you can ask me on [GitHub](https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues).

## Quick Start

### Create a new post

``` bash
$ hexo new "My New Post"
```

More info: [Writing](https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html)

### Run server

``` bash
$ hexo server
```

More info: [Server](https://hexo.io/docs/server.html)

### Generate static files

``` bash
$ hexo generate
```

More info: [Generating](https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html)

### Deploy to remote sites

``` bash
$ hexo deploy
```

More info: [Deployment](https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html)

Post.title: 创建一个Spring Boot 项目
Post._content:
# 创建一个 Spring Boot 项目

## 打开 Spring Initializr 网页

[Spring Initializr](https://start.spring.io)

## 配置项目信息
- Project: Maven
- Language: Java
- Spring Boot: 3.5.x
- Project Metadata :
    - Group: com.gnerv
    - Artifact: demo01
    - Name: demo01
    - Description: Demo project for Spring Boot
    - Package name: com.gnerv.demo01
    - Packaging: jar
    - Configuration: Properties
    - Java: 21
- Dependencies: 
    - Spring Boot DevTools
    - Lombok
    - Spring Configuration Processor
    - Spring Web
### 如下图所示
![alt text](1-创建项目/image.png)

## 下载项目文件
### 点击[GENERATE]按钮下载项目文件
![alt text](1-创建项目/image-1.png)

## 打开项目文件
### 解压文件,使用Idea打开项目文件夹,点击运行按钮启动项目

![alt text](1-创建项目/image-2.png)

::: tip
控制台显示以上内容表示项目正常启动。
:::
